ECB - Electronic Code Book
The message is divided into blocks, and each block is encrypted separately. 

                    PLAINTEXT                                       PLAINTEXT
                        |                                               |
                        v                                               v
    KEY ->   block_cipher_encryption                KEY ->   block_cipher_encryption
                        |                                               |
                        v                                               v
                    CIPHERTEXT                                      CIPHERTEXT
